Type: Package
Package: coil20
Title: Download COIL-20 and COIL-100 Object Image Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: person("James", "Melville", email = "jlmelville@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download the processed COIL-20 and COIL-100 object image
    datasets from the Columbia University Image Library and convert them to
    row-based R objects. Also provides a helper for viewing individual images.
